-- Bernard Madoff arrested by FBI: report
-- 
-- Thu Dec 11, 2008 4:49pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/11/us-madoff-idUSTRE4BA71B20081211

 

 (Reuters) - Bernard Madoff was arrested by the FBI on Thursday and charged with criminal securities fraud, the Wall Street Journal reported. 

 Highlight: * Criminal complaint against Madoff alleges he told senior employees that firm was giant ponzi scheme-wsj, citing source